4:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6 line-clamp-3 flex-grow","children":"Experience the magic of the Galapagos in 5 days. Visit the lush highlands of Santa Cruz to see giant tortoises, explore the volcanic landscapes of Isabela Island, and snorkel with white-tip reef sharks and penguins in Tintoreras. A perfect blend of adventure and relaxation."}]
